quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  110,1,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Igihe habonetse intsinzi y’Imana Allah ugatsinda ababangikanyamana mu Bakorayishi, ugaheza ugahabuza igisagara ca Makka;"
  110,2,"Ukabona n’abantu binjira mw’idini ry’Imana Allah ry’ubwislamu ari benshi mu migwimigwi;"
  110,3,"Aho rero, uraca witegurira kurengutswa n’Imana Allah, uheze uninahaze ushimagize Imana yawe Rurema Allah, wongere uyisabe kenshi ikigongwe. Mu vy’ukuri, Yo Yamye Yumvira cane abigaya."
